Package <Unnamed>

Class Summary
Controller Controller is the "brain" of each taxi and is the class that removes and adds taxis to the system Enables dispatcher Controller contains the location list which determines the locations of each taxi
ControllerThread This is a thread setup by the controller for communicating with taxis viathe network.
DetArea This is a class consisting of only static methods and variables.
DisControl This is a class containing a thread used when calling cabs.
DispatchUI GUI for Dispatcher (DisControl) Contains inputs and controls for regestering a taxi request.
Location This class is an object containing the necessary data for a location int ew and ns are the coordinates for east-west (ew) streets and north-south (ns) streets.
Request this class is an object used by the dispatcher (DisControl) to store requests.
Taxi Starts TaxiThread (a new taxi) in a specified area Listens for requests form the disparcher (DisControl).
TaxiThread This class contains a thread that controls a specific taxi.
TaxiUI GUI for taxi.
